text: National Highway 332A, commonly referred to as NH 332A is a national highway in India. It is a secondary route of National Highway 32. NH-332A runs in the state of Tamil Nadu in India. == Route == NH332A connects Puducherry and Mamallapuram in the state of Tamil Nadu. == Junctions == : Terminal near Puducherry. == See also == * List of National Highways in India * List of National Highways in India by state == References == == External links == * NH 332A on OpenStreetMap Category:National highways in India Category:National Highways in Tamil Nadu
